    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214280/extras/e787e4309d3a71a0fb0772aed6fc91a3.avif?t=1771921932\" width=672 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从零开始打造属于你的夜市——想摆什么摊位全由你决定，自由又热闹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214280/extras/abc20680a9c70aaa2f61f5e50526529d.poster.avif?t=1771921932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214280/extras/abc20680a9c70aaa2f61f5e50526529d.webm?t=1771921932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214280/extras/abc20680a9c70aaa2f61f5e50526529d.mp4?t=1771921932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214280/extras/bf98bbe05ddd1462ab9620140e28c236.webp?t=1771921932\" width=1040 height=17 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214280/extras/358c47307a6734a2659aa33e83241e47.avif?t=1771921932\" width=672 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顾客喜欢甜一点？还是更爱咸香？推理出最佳答案，找到让人一试就上瘾的秘密调味！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214280/extras/ea7d4650d53b4664d49be8553c853b8f.poster.avif?t=1771921932\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214280/extras/ea7d4650d53b4664d49be8553c853b8f.webm?t=1771921932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=